node.text: since beginning this journey of nugget #2, I've been focusing more on more natural products, and as a #teamipartner I am SO excited to show you guys some of my newest faves🤗  I'm obsessed with this serum right now from @teamiblends! it's made with hibiscus🌺 which is great to tightening skin & vitamin c so it really leaves my skin hydrated and plump, which is perf because I also use it as a primer and it lays the most flawless foundation. I also make sure to keep all my products in my skincare fridge, it's so relaxing waking up to cool skincare, especially if i'm a lil puffy, it helps take the inflammation away. (huge baby momma hack!) I really suggest everyone look into this, it's been a life savor since I switched! I have 30% off for their holiday sale, use MAE30 for 30% off babes #thankyouteami
